reviews.subject: Mathematics
reviews.review: Dr. Johnson is an excellent professor who explains concepts clearly and is always available for extra help.

reviews.subject: Computer Science
reviews.review: Prof. Smith is very knowledgeable and makes complex topics easy to understand. Highly recommended!

reviews.subject: Biology
reviews.review: Dr. Williams is good, but the lectures can be a bit dry at times. The material is still well covered.

reviews.subject: Chemistry
reviews.review: Dr. Brown is engaging and makes chemistry interesting. Labs are well-organized and informative.

reviews.subject: Physics
reviews.review: Prof. Davis's lectures are hard to follow. Needs to work on clarity and organization.

reviews.subject: Economics
reviews.review: Dr. Miller is fantastic. His real-world examples make economics easy to grasp and enjoyable.

reviews.subject: History
reviews.review: Prof. Wilson is very passionate about history. Her classes are engaging and well-structured.

reviews.subject: English Literature
reviews.review: Dr. Moore's classes are insightful but can be quite challenging. Requires a lot of reading.

reviews.subject: Philosophy
reviews.review: Prof. Taylor encourages critical thinking and discussion. Her lectures are thought-provoking and stimulating.

reviews.subject: Political Science
reviews.review: Dr. Anderson is very knowledgeable and passionate about politics. Classes are interactive and engaging.

reviews.subject: Psychology
reviews.review: Prof. Thomas is good but sometimes the material is presented in a disorganized manner.

reviews.subject: Sociology
reviews.review: Dr. Jackson provides a comprehensive understanding of sociology. His lectures are well-organized and insightful.

reviews.subject: Art History
reviews.review: Prof. Martinez brings art history to life with her engaging teaching style and deep knowledge.

reviews.subject: Engineering
reviews.review: Dr. Lee is knowledgeable but his lectures are often confusing and unstructured.

reviews.subject: Statistics
reviews.review: Prof. Robinson makes complex statistics concepts easier to understand with her clear explanations.

reviews.subject: Environmental Science
reviews.review: Dr. Walker covers the material well but his lectures can be a bit monotonous.

reviews.subject: Business Administration
reviews.review: Prof. Lewis provides valuable insights into business practices and is very approachable.

reviews.subject: Linguistics
reviews.review: Dr. Young is an excellent linguistics professor who makes learning fun and engaging.

reviews.subject: Music
reviews.review: Prof. Wright is very enthusiastic about music and his classes are both educational and enjoyable.

reviews.subject: Law
reviews.review: Dr. Harris's classes are informative but can be quite demanding and fast-paced.

reviews.subject: Theater
reviews.review: Prof. Clark is incredibly passionate about theater and brings a lot of energy to her classes.
